{"tid":1179424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【嫌坐月價cheap】大陸網民笑吳奇隆孤寒 婦科名醫：抱歉台灣醫療太便宜","createTime":"2019-05-31T06:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T18:38:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5f0dacab0835627fb08c0b539448b9430db65191","tid":1179424,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:06:11.000Z","msg":"48歲吳奇隆及32歲中國女星劉詩詩結婚4年，上月27日劉詩詩在台北誕下「小奇隆」，先傳出劉詩詩跟婆婆不合，疑似患產後抑鬱症，而吳奇隆日花1.2萬元台幣（約3千港元）讓劉詩詩坐月子，被大陸網民笑他孤寒。<br />\n台灣婦科名醫蘇怡寧昨晚在facebook發文向吳奇隆道歉：「四爺很抱歉，因為台灣醫療太便宜害你被中國網民酸（寸）了。」他指出如果月子中心要求像頂級飯店一樣比較奢華及寬敞，「對不起，在台灣我們不玩這個，要比這個那你生小孩去飯店生好了，杜拜不錯」。<br />\n蘇怡寧稱「如果要談到醫療的本質，我必須很驕傲的說，台灣人，我們真的是很幸福的」，他提到「之前一直笑着跟別人說，台灣跟大陸醫療的費用差不多，只是後面的幣值不一樣，一個是新台幣一個是人民幣，然後笑着笑着就哭了」。<br />\n他反問每天都有中國人來台就醫，難道不是相信台灣醫療品質，又問大陸網民是否知道每個月有多少中國醫療機構要來台灣「取經」，蘇怡寧又說其實沒甚麼值得爭辯，「四爺是寵妻才會留在台灣的，你識貨」，他在文尾表示：「我台灣人我驕傲」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190530/large/1559214183_6903.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190530%2Flarge%2F1559214183_6903.jpg&h=dd055c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190530/large/1559213914_16ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190530%2Flarge%2F1559213914_16ac.jpg&h=d46f7988&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190530/59658921\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190530%2F59658921&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoKhYowssEfWxGXKUUX6%2FcpY%3D&h=008da19a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190530%2F59658921&h=cef82b0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190530/59658921</a>"},{"pid":"4296d3b3f450f4e50c8ce75f34333b99a0bced6f","tid":1179424,"uid":229549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"姑娘，地下成地玻璃呀"},{"pid":"601b80ef2aad124948b33db8ad09de6ac9490860","tid":1179424,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"呆灣基礎醫療一定好過港中"},{"pid":"26dacf0f61c71bd7fa96af75d77d81d37f04f0a5","tid":1179424,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"601b80ef2aad124948b33db8ad09de6ac9490860","tid":1179424,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T11:09:50.000Z","msg":"呆灣基礎醫療一定好過港中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:33:29.000Z","msg":"香港既話 有錢就有命 窮人就等收皮<br />\n賭王就係一個人板"},{"pid":"bdd90e3528607e00aacdebe926c74670a096386d","tid":1179424,"uid":3962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:38:28.000Z","msg":"台灣醫療亞洲top嫁喎唔通上去醫埋單小左個腎呀肝咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}